cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD

This paper is about building AI agents for interactive systems, specifically for dynamic search. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with text retrieval and compression, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of Reinforcement Learning (RL) and linear approximation for document retrieval also indicates that it could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
